Task 4. Imagine that you are doing a project "Celebrating the New Year" together with your friend. You have found some illustrations and want to share the news. Leave a voice message to your friend.
In 2.5 minutes be ready to:
- give a brief description of the photos, justifying the choice of the photos for the project;
- say in what way the pictures are different, justifying the choice of the photos for the project;
- mention the advantages and disadvantages (1-2) of the two ways of celebrating the New Year;
- express your opinion on the subject of the project - whether you prefer to celebrate the New Year at home and why.
You will speak for not more than 3 minutes (12-15 sentences).
You have to talk continuously.

